videos.description: Maryland's Bruno Fernando leaps and jams the pick-and-roll alley-oop from Anthony Cowan Jr. in the first half.
videos.headline: Fernando slams home alley-oop for Maryland

videos.description: Maryland forward Jalen Smith's layup trickles off the rim, but Bruno Fernando is there to springboard and flush the miss.
videos.headline: Fernando cleans up garbage on putback dunk

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter whips a quick pass to a diving Jack Salt, who rattles the rim on a two-handed stuff.
videos.headline: Virginia's Salt adds pepper to two-handed dunk

videos.description: Maryland capitalizes on a gritty defensive stand as Eric Ayala feeds Bruno Fernando on the other end for a ferocious dunk.
videos.headline: Fernando wrecks rim on vicious jam

videos.description: Virginia's Kyle Guy hits De'Andre Hunter on the fast break, who skies and slams the right-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Hunter clear for takeoff on tomahawk stuff
